  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My mother, perhaps in a completely autodidact way, because she had-- I said she had no opportunity for schooling-- became a highly intelligent, extremely knowledgeable, and very literate intellectual, to the point where she literally maintained what perhaps in different circumstances and in a different age would have been called a salon.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Our house became a kind of a, almost a debating society, where all the town's intellectuals congregated, literally sitting at her feet, and where intellectual [INAUDIBLE] [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] had been flying day and night, virtually, which in and of itself, had a tremendous impact on me and on my sisters because obviously, we couldn't be kept out of it.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We wouldn't, we wouldn't go to bed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we wouldn't leave [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the room where this fiery debate and discussion of, of the world and all its ills were being discussed, analyzed, taken apart, and put back together.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My mother, who was obviously a completely observant Jew and wore a sheitel, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was nonetheless [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] really the most sophisticated, and as far as we, the children, are concerned, certainly the most complete, the most completely human being that we have ever known, the most civilized and wisest of all people, as far as we are concerned.",
      "word_count": 68
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And this holds true for my sisters, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She never died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we sort of spend our life trying to measure up to what may be our idealized ideal of her and measure our lives and our actions to her standards to this day.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her name was Treza Halpert, T-R-E-Z-A, H-A-L-P-E-R-T.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She had a tremendous impact not only on us but on, on the wider surroundings.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
